      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideal for a major restoration project or as a parts donor. The engine suffers from a blown head gasket and significant oil leaks, and the transmission is currently non-functional in higher gears. The exterior displays widespread rust, particularly on the frame and wheel wells, along with multiple deep scratches and dents. Inside, the cabin requires a complete overhaul due to heavily damaged upholstery and non-working electronics; it is not roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
