    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this impeccably preserved masterpiece. Presented in true showroom condition, every detail of this vehicle reflects a legacy of meticulous care and pride of ownership. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, this car offers an unrivaled driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new. A rare find for the enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection and long-term value.",
      "price": 48500.0,
